data.description: Welcome to Waterstone's gem—a 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, two-story single-family home. This spacious, sunlit haven offers numerous upgrades like accordion shutters, flooring, a new A/C unit, and an LED-lit patio cover. With one of the community's largest backyards, you'll enjoy outdoor serenity. Waterstone's amenities include two pools, a children's pool, a clubhouse, a gym, and lakeside vistas, all safeguarded by a 24/7 security guard. The community is located next to The Waterstone Charter School and close to Homestead Airbase, Baptist Hospital, highways, shopping, and dining.
